Description
===========

Imports a CLI session from an archive.


Usage
=====

   oci session import [OPTIONS]


Required Parameters
===================

--session-archive [path]

The session archive to import.


Optional Parameters
===================

--force

If the profile being imported already exists, overwrite the existing
profile without a confirmation prompt.
